West of Zanzibar (1954 - UK)

Adventure
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0047669/


Made by Ealing Studios in Zanzibar, Tanzania

When their region suffers a drought, the rural Galana tribe move to Mombasa. The tribe's peaceful ways are destroyed by the influence of illegal ivory traders. Game warden, Bob Payton, turns detective travelling to Zanzibar to discover the ringleader behind the ivory smuggling. Payton tracks his quarry through some of the most treacherous passages of the Zanzibar territory.
